{"tid":556301,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(maths)排列&組合,呢條點計?","createTime":"2018-02-10T11:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T14:43:35.000Z","uid":37620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61f086cb992bd9e8b637016ef155bfad4445544b","tid":556301,"uid":37620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"Q:從6名男士和7名女士中安排5人負責5項不同的工作。<br />\nA.安排5名女士負責5項不同的工作，有多少種方法?<br />\nB.安排最少1名男士負責5項不同的工作，有多少種方法?<br />\n<br />\nA part ans: 7P5=2520 呢題ok<br />\n<br />\nB part答案係151920，我試過兩種方法做:<br />\n<br />\n方法1:<br />\n13P5 - 7P5 = 151920 呢個方法做到個答案<br />\n方法2:<br />\n安排最少1名男士=1男4女/2男3女/3男2女/4男1女/5男0女<br />\n1男4女=(6P1)(7P0)=5040<br />\n2男3女=(6P2)(7P0)=6300<br />\n3男2女=(6P3)(7P0)=5040<br />\n4男1女=(6P4)(7P0)=2520<br />\n5男0女=(6P5)(7P0)=720<br />\n以上加埋=5040+6300+5040+2520+720=19620<br />\n<br />\n方法2做唔到個答案，我做錯左邊度/諗漏邊啲case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"498d6ce432c5b0615151796a9425fd459e768df1","tid":556301,"uid":23798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"0女又7P0<br />\n4女又7P0<br />\n計數機又篤錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d31eb7348b48f56f6eee4222dfe0596400e3e9e","tid":556301,"uid":135986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498d6ce432c5b0615151796a9425fd459e768df1","tid":556301,"uid":23798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"0女又7P0<br />\n4女又7P0<br />\n計數機又篤錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"(6p1)(7p4)<br />\netc."},{"pid":"5d8b4cd25837c271dac2abcfac7d9c44cd6a2cc1","tid":556301,"uid":37620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0女又7P0<br />\n4女又7P0<br />\n計數機又篤錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsor手殘 我打錯數字<br />\n1男4女=(6P1)